<br>
I cleared the room, then had everyone move in to the right of the room. I pulled with dispell, then immediately Deftdanced. I then HoS'd him and slowed him, then dispelled one more time before deftdance wore off.<br>
<br>
But right after I got him slowed, our tank got immediately rampaged to death, even after activating his Defensive discipline. I don't know how this happened, since he has 10k HPs and the max hit he got on me was 1890. The shaman went next, then he killed the pet, then turned on us one by one. He was at 20% when we had all died.<br>
<br>
So my question is, what do I do about this guy? If he can kill a defensive 10k warrior with just rampage, how are we supposed to kill him? I was thinking that he could stay out of ramp range until my disc was just about to wear off, then activate his auto-riposte discipline (which lasts for 8 seconds), and hopefully the named would be dead by then.<br>
<br>
